{"continue": {"iistart": "2012-04-21T18:36:28Z", "continue": "||"}, "query": {"pages": {"11264065": {"pageid": 11264065, "ns": 6, "title": "File:Charles Darwin seated crop.jpg", "imagerepository": "local", "imageinfo": [{"size": 1230334, "width": 2370, "height": 3119, "canonicaltitle": "File:Charles Darwin seated crop.jpg", "url": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/2e/Charles_Darwin_seated_crop.jpg", "descriptionurl": "https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Charles_Darwin_seated_crop.jpg", "descriptionshorturl": "https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?curid=11264065", "extmetadata": {"DateTime": {"value": "2012-04-21 19:18:57", "source": "mediawiki-metadata", "hidden": ""}, "ObjectName": {"value": "Charles Darwin seated crop", "source": "mediawiki-metadata"}, "CommonsMetadataExtension": {"value": 1.2, "source": "extension", "hidden": ""}, "Categories": {"value": "Author died more than 70 years ago public domain images|Maull & Fox|Portraits of Charles Darwin|PD US expired|CC-PD-Mark|Uploaded with derivativeFX|Male people sitting indoors", "source": "commons-categories", "hidden": ""}, "Assessments": {"value": "", "source": "commons-categories", "hidden": ""}, "ImageDescription": {"value": "Photograph of Charles Darwin; the frontispiece of <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Francis_Darwin\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Francis Darwin\">Francis Darwin</a>'s <i><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Life_and_Letters_of_Charles_Darwin\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:The Life and Letters of Charles Darwin\">The Life and Letters of Charles Darwin</a></i> (1887) has the caption \"From a Photograph (1854?) by Messrs. Maull. And Fox. Engraved for <i>Harper's Magazine</i>, October 1884.\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">[</span>1<span class=\"cite-bracket\">]</span></a></sup>  In an 1899 paper, Francis Darwin wrote that \"The date of the photograph is probably 1854; it is, however, impossible